Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:09.73,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.29,DogDays-ep-title,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)\an1}Homecoming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:49.40,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Verde!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:50.29,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.27,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.20,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this song is being sung,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:01.68,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't maintain my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.43,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.35,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:09.16,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make your dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.74,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:11.94,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:12.84,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.44,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:15.44,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.29,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The healing song is purifying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:25.95,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.11,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.46,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,A disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.49,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.19,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sharl, I'm asking you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.84,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's still things I need \Nto talk to him about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.64,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Then use your hero crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:54.26,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,You can use defensive techniques \Nto shut out the power of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.37,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.28,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.15,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me for whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.33,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Crystals,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:04.97,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.54,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you could use them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:23.16,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't hear the song anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.99,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.88,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.57,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.49,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't paying enough attention to Verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.94,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:51.04,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed of going to the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:55.53,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and all Verde did was try to \Nmake that wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.41,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.58,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.62,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,or the details of what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.56,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,but no matter the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.04,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,a man must never make a woman cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.70,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you did do something wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.90,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,but just crying and apologizing \Nwon't help anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.01,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:46.26,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,it's not a bad thing to \Nhave dreams or hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.27,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.71,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I made you sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.77,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.28,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a demon. A disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.88,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're a demon or a disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.29,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,you're still Verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.71,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You were always with me when I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:18.41,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You were always thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.83,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to do everything you could for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.54,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.93,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,kind Verde that I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:43.44,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.56,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.62,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.57,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That light is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.46,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,A cursed blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.21,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.63,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.96,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He was possessed by a cursed blade, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.15,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:10.09,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes of the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.65,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.21,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.32,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.61,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.43,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Verde will slowly regain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:47.33,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,his original form inside this crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.95,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.17,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,originally a high-level spirit \Nor a local god's servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.34,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The cursed blade possessed him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.89,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and turned him into a \NSickness Demon Disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.54,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Normally it would take
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:05.28,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,a very long time for him to regain \Nhis original form, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.93,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep him by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.63,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and sing him gentle songs all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.94,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,he may wake up fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.36,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:17.91,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.60,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Her voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.42,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.07,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Aria-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.52,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.63,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:56.77,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too, princess of the surface world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.77,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Millihiore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.58,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Songstress of the Sky Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.67,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I will sing a song of healing as the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.66,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,songstress of the Star Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.96,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Millihiore, will you sing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.92,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.46,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big help, Couver-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.50,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:03.65,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,People of the surface, \Nand Dragon Priestess Sharl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:07.29,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,once again, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.49,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It took a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.78,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,but I was able to find the Fire Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.78,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.58,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Now we don't have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.78,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.81,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.36,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.52,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.54,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to give you a sign of thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.86,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,for your courage and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.56,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.85,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I believe on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.94,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,you call it a Phantasmal \NBeast or a Divine Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.33,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Phantasmal Beasts are truly legendary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.21,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're said to be servants of the gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.56,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,and just seeing them will \Nbring you good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.95,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones I've ever seen are
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.83,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Pega and this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.45,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Pega is one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:07.74,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he looked like that \Nbefore he transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:11.33,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He'll look like that too, \Nonce he transforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.57,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I will give him to you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.13,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,as a sign of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.72,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:26.10,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's taken a liking to Prince Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.72,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.91,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful, Prince Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:33.08,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Then as a representative of \Nthe Tri-country Alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:36.48,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,we'll keep him in Galette. \NWill that be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.99,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that would be ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.40,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like keeping a phantasmal beast
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.20,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,would be a scary experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:56.63,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:11.20,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.40,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.00,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.90,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.41,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aria-san is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.33,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.20,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Couver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.36,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Can you head over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.41,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.58,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We should all say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.69,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, Prince Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.23,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She saved your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.14,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,so go yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.33,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.48,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.82,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second time you've saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:13.87,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You and your friends saved me and Verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.57,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of things\NI wanted to talk about, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.26,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.13,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.74,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me, and I saved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.08,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,and we both went on an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:35.65,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend now, just like all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.12,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Same with Verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.28,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you and everyone else again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.22,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.42,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.80,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go see you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.38,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:52.79,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.25,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.79,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.37,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to see us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.99,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,that's a good enough reason to come see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:04.99,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need any reason \Nto want to see someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.30,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,or be with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.24,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.57,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.69,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:30.06,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking good back \Nthere, weren't you, Gaul?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.44,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.46,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I just said goodbye, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.71,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.98,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It was great, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:38.96,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.45,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Aria-san can come \Nto the surface to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.94,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.12,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're far apart, \Nas long as you're thinking of each other
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.09,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,the bonds between you won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.55,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,But to keep those bonds strong it's best to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:55.10,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,see the people you care \Nabout once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.60,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:03.37,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're almost outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.91,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Dragon is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.36,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.12,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.06,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for putting you through all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.05,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.13,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Come see us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:56.04,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the Sky Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.85,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,will always welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.58,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:07.30,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but everybody's safe, \Nand it's peaceful again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.49,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to do enough fighting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.68,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, Eclair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.77,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,No, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:18.81,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing to not have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.92,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to restore peace \Nwithout anyone being hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.81,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.56,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.32,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're almost beneath the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.17,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:40.49,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The light falls down here, too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.95,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.94,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I've never actually seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:47.76,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too. I've only heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:51.22,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably falling on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:54.59,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the people on the \Nsurface are very confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.36,DogDays-narrator,N,0000,0000,0000,,And so our adventures in the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.36,DogDays-narrator,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Sea came to a safe end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:13.07,DogDays-narrator,N,0000,0000,0000,,The princesses explained what the \Nstrange presence from the sky was,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.72,DogDays-narrator,N,0000,0000,0000,,and that it would continue for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.82,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,So this light is a present from
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.95,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,the Star Whale in the Sky Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:27.26,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.92,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely rare natural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.63,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,When nightfall comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.65,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,drink and watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:48.50,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It went by so fast again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.90,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,But a lot happened, and every day was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.11,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,You can come back next time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.01,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.73,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,I can come on long weekends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.91,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,And I can plan my weekends \Naround the war games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.53,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.04,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This time I got to take a vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.77,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,so next time I have to do my \Njob as a Hero in the games!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.67,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! \NAs leader, I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.17,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.16,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,so I can be an official ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.51,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cheering you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.90,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:19.85,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.56,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason I don't feel very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:26.22,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:30.31,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,We can always talk, and we can \Nsee each other whenever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.75,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But once I get back and I'm alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.84,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.37,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:39.36,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.15,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:41.58,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:45.70,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.05,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:50.96,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't we be good friends, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.68,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We're both heirs to the Hero King, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.59,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:01.53,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... what else am I forgetting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.73,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.80,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present from Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.20,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.20,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if you forget something,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.50,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,you can come get it back quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.74,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something Jamie can carry,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.24,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,he can hop back and forth quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.32,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:24.37,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to leave \Nwith my room a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.37,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,As Galette's Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.37,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,it's kind of embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.13,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.85,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's hurry and get it cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.38,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.23,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. \NOkay, Hero Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.09,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.62,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Cou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.89,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.65,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you didn't \Nforget anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.90,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.41,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,The way things happened last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.90,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make sure things go okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.24,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.66,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home safe and come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:01.83,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.66,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Shinku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:09.66,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:13.54,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,What Nanami-san and Rebecca-san \Nsaid to Aria-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:18.17,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a reason to want to see \Nsomeone, or to want to be with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:22.25,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?\NThat that's what you told
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:25.08,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca-san a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:29.43,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It was a long time ago, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.81,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of remember, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.11,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,When she was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:39.06,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,every time there was a long vacation, \Nshe would be so happy to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:41.40,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,but she was worried you might
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.57,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,want to play with somebody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:46.18,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,or that you were bored when you were with her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.92,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,because she wasn't good at sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.51,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.14,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So she didn't say what she was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:57.29,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Becky was so quiet when she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.71,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,But she says
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.72,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,you told her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.96,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,"You can come see me just \Nbecause you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.63,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy and having fun when
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.97,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you, Becky."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.61,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It made her very happy, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.70,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.90,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't spent a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.73,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,time with you, Shinku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.11,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.43,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:35.31,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to keep playing with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.47,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.51,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.20,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.21,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.61,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are we home safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.50,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:06.40,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What about Becky?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.87,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:10.12,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Shinku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.91,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.75,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.86,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.30,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.88,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do our jobs here on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:24.69,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,and get ready to go back to Flognarde!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:25.64,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.85,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give my studies and \Nsports everything I've got!
